namespace Javax.Naming

Contains .NET proxy types for Java classes from the package javax.naming.

See:
          Description

Type Summary
Binding .NET proxy type for class javax.naming.Binding.
This class represents a name-to-object binding found in a context.
Context .NET proxy type for interface javax.naming.Context.
This interface represents a naming context, which consists of a set of name-to-object bindings.
InitialContext .NET proxy type for class javax.naming.InitialContext.
This class is the starting context for performing naming operations.
Name .NET proxy type for interface javax.naming.Name.
The Name interface represents a generic name -- an ordered sequence of components.
NameClassPair .NET proxy type for class javax.naming.NameClassPair.
This class represents the object name and class name pair of a binding found in a context.
NameParser .NET proxy type for interface javax.naming.NameParser.
This interface is used for parsing names from a hierarchical namespace.
NamingEnumeration .NET proxy type for interface javax.naming.NamingEnumeration.
This interface is for enumerating lists returned by methods in the javax.naming and javax.naming.directory packages.
NamingException .NET proxy type for class javax.naming.NamingException.
This is the superclass of all exceptions thrown by operations in the Context and DirContext interfaces.
